Class MethodInterceptorInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.schlimm.springcdi.interceptor.model.InterceptorInfo
      com.schlimm.springcdi.interceptor.model.MethodInterceptorInfo

public class MethodInterceptorInfo
extends InterceptorInfo

Subclass of InterceptorInfo that defines logic specific to JSR 318/299 business method interceptors. Assumes that BeanDefinition of BeanDefinitionHolder is of type AnnotatedBeanDefinition.

Author:
Niklas Schlimm
